title: BRIEF-Vinfast Trading & Investment Pte Ltd Files For U.S. IPO
text:
* VINFAST TRADING & INVESTMENT PTE SAYS WILL CONVERT TO SINGAPORE PUBLIC LIMITED CO; UPON CONVERSION, CO WILL BE KNOWN AS VINFAST AUTO LTD

* VINFAST TRADING & INVESTMENT PTE SAYS INTENDS TO APPLY TO LIST VINFAST AUTO LTD'S ORDINARY SHARES ON NASDAQ UNDER SYMBOL “VFS”

* VINFAST TRADING & INVESTMENT PTE SAYS CITIGROUP, MORGAN STANLEY, CREDIT SUISSE, J.P. MORGAN ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO VINFAST AUTO LTD'S U.S. IPO

* VINFAST TRADING & INVESTMENT-BNP PARIBAS, HSBC, RBC CAPITAL MARKETS, WOLFE NOMURA ALLIANCE ARE ALSO AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO VINFAST AUTO LTD'S U.S. IPO
